{
  "stem": "5356.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But people, in my time, were still observing, you know, the day that he died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From all over Poland, they used to come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the city was full of life-- with the scribes sitting in the city to write, you know, notes to go out and put down.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The notes-- you know, everybody [? requested ?] [? it. ?] It's the same way as, you know, they do it in Kotel Maraavi, in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The same thing happened the days when-- yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, the city consisted of-- it was divided the upper part, and the lower part, and it was four streets.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then when had-- in my time, we had a beautiful center of the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was called the mark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It had nice stores, and it was a beautiful garden built, you know, and where the animal kept in there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were benches around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were people used to-- to walk and sit-- and have benches to sit down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it came, a Friday afternoon, all the stores were closed because 99% of-- were Jewish owned.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And everybody-- not everybody went to services, but about 90% of the people were observant.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember we used to go, my father to Friday night services, then, when we came home, we sat down to the table.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Nine people, you know, to have a Friday night meal and sing Zemirot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 18 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, those are things that you can't-- [CRYING]",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What you can't forget Saturday mornings, when we went to services.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had friends that used to come in-- [CRYING] Saturday morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had Shabbat tea, you know, before going to services because you're not allowed to eat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And coming on for the services, you know, the Shabbat meal consisted of cholent.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
